name: Akfix  610 PU Express Montage Adhesive Transparent
short_description:
"Akfix 610 is a single component, fast curing polyurethane based adhesive. It combines high bond strength with fast curing. The water resistance property makes it exceptionally good at bonding wooden surfaces where water splash and moisture is an issue.


Properties
Fast curing, low press time.
Conforms to D4 according to DIN EN 204.
Transparent.
Extremely high bond strength on wooden substrates.
Thixotropic, non-sag, ideal for vertical joints.
Low consumption, economical.
Usable on slightly wet substrates.
Very good resistance to chemicals.
Excellent resistance to moisture and weather conditions.
Good filling properties.
Non-shrinking.
Low odor.

Applications Area
It is suitable for use in construction and repair applications where a permanent strong bond is required between porous-porous and porousnonporous surfaces.
Bonding wooden surfaces at bathroom, kitchens, decks etc. where there is a constant moisture and water contact risk.
It can be used for bonding various kinds of construction materials such as wood, MDF, concrete, metal, polystyrene and polyurethane foam, marble, granite and ceramic etc."

  • Type : Shopping Bags & Trolleys
  • Brand : Akfix

name: Akfix  MS Polymer High Tack Shore A55
short_description:
• Type : Tapes & Adhesives
  • Brand : Akfix
"Akfix All Bond MS High Tack is a MS polymer-based, one component, high quality and professional adhesive with high adhesive strength and initial tack. It is suitable for bonding heavy building materials without the use of clamps and/or fixing tape

Properties
High initial grab,
Does not contain solvent, silicone or isocyanate,
Semi-elastic bonding,
Very good UV resistance
Excellent elasticity and very good adhesion strength
Over-paintable with water based paints,
No bubble formation
No shrinkage
Primer less adhesion on many different substrates (preliminary test recommended)

Applications Area
Wall cladding elements and ceiling panels
Sound isolation panels (mineral wool, wood-wool cement & plastic foams)
Thermal isolation panels (PUR, PIR, PS)
Casings and frames in building construction
Wooden and plastic laths, ornaments and frames
Doorsteps, window sills, skirting boards and cover plates
Complete construction elements (such as roofing and facade elements) in frame."

name: Akfix  MS Polymer Clear Shore A35
short_description:
• Type : Tapes & Adhesives
  • Brand : Akfix
"All Bond MS Clear; is a high quality, neutral, elastic, crystal clear elastic adhesive based on MS polymer.

Properties
Crystal clear permanently elastic formulation.
High bond strength nearly on all surfaces even if slightly humid.
Very good mechanical properties.
Do not contain solvent, silicone, isocyanate, halogens or acids.
Good extrudability even at low temperatures.
Over-paintable with water based paints.
Primerless adhesion to numerous porous and non-porous substrates.
No shrinkage.
Does not crack or discolor.

Applications Area
It has a good adhesive strength without primer on most common materials  such as aluminum, zinc, galvanized steel, stainless steel, copper, natural   stone, concrete, brick, etc.
For crystal clear elastic bonding in construction and building applications.
Invisible bonding and sealing of glass and other transparent materials in indoor applications."

short_description:
• Type : Tapes & Adhesives
  • Brand : Akfix
"Akfix 840 is a self-extinguishable aerosol polyurethane foam for filling, sealing and bonding gaps. It is designed for easy dispensing through the straw adapter included to each can.

Properties
Rated B2 according to DIN 4102.
Excellent adhesion to most building materials.
It does not contain any propellant gases that are harmful to the ozone layer.
It can be painted after curing.
It can be cut and sawn.  

Applications Area
Fixing and insulating of door and window frames.
Filling and sealing of gaps, joints and cavities.
Filling of penetrations in walls.
Insulating electrical outlets and water pipes."

short_description:
• Type : Tapes & Adhesives
  • Brand : Akfix
"Akfix 805 is a single-component, moisture-curing and self-expanding aerosol polyurethane foam. It is designed for easy dispensing through the straw adapter included with each can. It does not contain any propellant gases that are harmful to the ozone layer.

Properties
Excellent adhesion & filling capacity and high thermal & acoustical insulation value.
Excellent mounting capacity and stability.
Adheres to almost all building materials with the exception of surfaces such as polyethylene, Teflon, silicone and surfaces contaminated with oils and greases, mold release agents and similar materials.
Mould-proof, water-proof, over paintable.
Cured foam dries rigid and can be trimmed, shaped and sanded. 

Applications Area
Fixing and insulating of door and window frames.
Filling and sealing gaps, joints and cavities.
Filling of penetrations in walls.
?Insulating electrical outlets and water pipes."

name: Akfix  705 Universal Fast Adhesive 100 ml
short_description:
• Type : Tapes & Adhesives
  • Brand : Akfix
"An adhesive set which consists of high viscosity cyanoacrylate adhesive and activator.

Properties
High bonding strength.
Suitable for use on vertical surfaces as it will not drip or slump.
It is particularly suited to bonding difficult substrates which have a porous or uneven nature since it increases bonding strength by preventing the adhesive to be absorbed by the surface.

Applications Area
It is suitable for the bonding of a very wide range of materials, including acidic surfaces and some porous ones, where rapid bonding times are required.
Suitable for MDF, wood, chip wood, rubber, most plastics, leather and other common substrates.
Especially suitable for the applications where cure speed needs to be accelerated.
Although Akfix 705 has a degree of gap filling ability, it is generally recommended for use on close-fitting parts and fairly smooth, even surfaces."

Especially suitable for the applications where cure speed needs to be accelerated.
Although Akfix 705 has a degree of gap filling ability, it is generally recommended for use on close-fitting parts and fairly smooth, even surfaces."

name: Akfix  P635 PU Sealant Construction 600 ml Black
short_description:
• Type : Tapes & Adhesives
  • Brand : Akfix
"P635 is a one-component, medium-modulus polyurethane sealant that cures on exposure to atmospheric humidity. It possesses excellent adhesion to all typical construction materials such as cement based materials, brick, ceramic, glass, wood, galvanized and painted sheet iron and various plastics.


Properties
Possesses permanent elasticity.
25 % movement capability.
No surface tackiness after full cure.
Do not pick up dirt.
No shrinkage.
Cures bubble-free.
Enhanced storage stability.
No sagging  Thixotropic.
Can be applied with hand gun and tooled easily.
Paintable.

Applications Area
Expansion joints between many different construction materials.
Movement and connection joints in floors.
Indoor and outdoor applications for pedestrian and traffic areas.
Joints between prefabricated construction materials.
Sealing and bonding of ventilation ducts, gutters and spouts etc.
For expansion joints between pre-cast concrete panels."

name: Akfix  A40 Magic 200 ml
short_description:
• Type : Tapes & Adhesives
  • Brand : Akfix
"Akfix A40 is an Corrosion Inhibitor, Lubricant and Multi Purpose Protector aerosol Spray. Its special formula, combines many properties such as cleaning, lubricating, loosening rusted part, driving out moisture. It can be used in industrial, home and daily labors.

Properties
Ultimate penetrating ability
Loosens rusted or corroded bolts, nuts, cables and any other fasteners.
Greases and loosens door and window hinges, locks, and other fittings.
Decreases frictions and stops squeaks of pedals, chairs, windows, faucets and hinges.
Does not contain silicone and any dirt trap additives.
Drives the moist out of the surface and dries it out, thus provides longtime lubricating effect.
Protects metal parts against rust.
Provides maintenance by penetrating into surface and protects it against dirt.
Dissolves tar, gum, adhesive etc.
Permeates into grease and dirt and creates a protective film layer on the surface.

Applications Area
In all fittings, door and window mechanisms, locks, handles, hinges.
For annulling humidity on metallic surfaces of bikes, motorbikes, small motor vehicles, electronic contacts and other home tools such as drills, jigsaws, etc.
For loosening and activating rusted and jammed mechanisms.
Can be used as protective on surfaces vulnerable to water and rust.
For dissolving adhesive materials like tar, gum, adhesive tapes etc.
Can be used for cleaning and maintenance of weapons."

name: Dream Adore Essential Foam Mattress
short_description:
The Dream Adore Essential mattress is made of a superior ultra-elastic, hypoallergenic material, which offers the comfort we all need during sleep. The mattress is rigid, but comfortable, thus providing the orthopedic support that helps the spine to keep its natural position during sleep, to have a calm and relaxing sensation every night.

The interior of the Dream Adore Essential mattress is made of standard polyurethane foam, with a density of 28 kg/m³, this solution being ideal for maximum comfort during sleep.

The exterior of the mattress offers a cover made of fabric density of 264 gr/m2 and 100 % polyester composition. The cover is treated anti - mite, anti - bacterial and anti - allergic, it is not quilted, it is removable and washable at 30 degrees. Dream Adore Essential mattress has no springs, it is reversible and vacuum packed.

Technical details:
 Brand: Dream Adore
 Foam type: standard polyurethane foam
 Foam density (Kg/m3): 28
 Type of wadding: 100% polyesther
 Removable cover: YES
 Cufflings for ventilation: NO
 Anti-allergic: YES
 Anti-acaria: YES
 Height of foam (cm): 13
 Height of mattress including cover (cm): 15
 Warranty (years): 6
 Mattress type: no springs
 Cover textile: not quiltted, washable, 100% PES composition

name: Dream Adore Aloe Vera Viscoelastic Memory Foam Mattress
short_description:
Dream Adore Memory 14 + 4 offers the user maximum comfort, for a restful sleep every night.

The mattress interior is made of two foam layers, each having an essential role in the unity of and the benefits of the mattress.

The first layer with the height of 14 cm, the lower one, is made of high resilience polyurethane foam, with a density of 35 kg/m3. It represents the support layer, which gives the mattress, firmness and the body, necessary support. The upper part of this layer is processed using a CNC machine, these profiles providing the necessary ventilation between the high resilience polyurethane layer and the memory foam layer. In addition, this layer has 7 comfort zones which help the mattress to take over the body weight, offering support and comfort.

The second layer is made of viscoelastic memory foam with density of 50 kg/m3 and it is 4 cm high. This foam is temperature sensitive so that not only responds to body weight, but also to its temperature. The main role of this layer is to reduce pressure points by creating body footprint and offering maximum comfort for a restful sleep.

The mattress has an outside cover made of textile treated with micro capsules of Aloe Vera, natural product whose effects on the human body are well known: it contains at least 160 biological substances, including enzymes, vitamins, minerals, fatty acids and amino acids, and with scientifically proven positive effects on the skin. The treatment with Aloe Vera can offer a bio-energetic balance, resulting in a restful sleep. The fabric has a density of 264 g/m2 and 100 % polyester composition. The mattress cover is treated against mites, with antibacterial and anti-allergic properties. It is quilted with wadding of 100 gr/m2, it is removable and washable at 30 degrees.

Technical details:
 Brand: Dream Adore
 Foam type layer 1: 14 cm high resilience polyurethane foam
 Foam type layer 2: 4 cm high memory foam
 Foam density layer 1 (Kg/m3): 35
 Foam density layer 2 (Kg/m3): 50
 Type of wadding: 100% polyesther
 Removable cover: YES
 Cufflings for ventilation: NO
 Anti-allergic: YES
 Anti-acaria: YES
 Height of foam, total (cm): 18
 Height of mattress including cover (cm): 20
 Warranty (years): 6
 Mattress type: no springs
 Cover textile: quiltted textile with Aloe Vera micro-capsules, washable, 100% PES composition

name: Catan Basic Boradgame Arabic & English edition
short_description:
Catan (Settlers to its friends) is one of the most popular International games of the past decade, with the game and its expansions selling over 25 million copies worldwide.

Players are recent immigrants to the newly populated island of Catan. You can expand Catan, building settlements, roads, and cities, by harvesting commodities from the land around you. Trade goods with other players to get the resources you need, or use local seaports.

The first player to achieve 10 points from a combination of roads, settlements, and special cards wins.

The game is enjoyed as a fun pastime, but for children (and adults willing to learn), the game offers the opportunity to learn and practice many valuable skills. Here are seven skills that Settlers emphasizes, both for younger and older children.

For younger children (ages 10-14), here are four skills that the game helps develop: probability, negotiation, planning, competitive problem solving.

name: Camel Up Basic Boradgame Arabic & English edition
short_description:
Camel Up - basic game, Arabic/English edition

Witness the craziest camel race of all time, as things really go topsy-turvy when camels stack up and entire pyramids turn upside down.

As members of Egyptian high society, you gather in the desert with one simple goal: to gain the most money by backing the right camel to win a leg or even the entire race. However, in this race, its not just the lucky ones who can beat the odds. Reading the dynamics of the race and having a good sense of timing is just as important when it come to backing the right camels and taking the victory.

CAMEL UP is a simple, quick, and outrageously exciting family game that can be enjoyed by up to 8 players.

short_description:
Four different diseases are outbreaking across the globe and its now up to you and your team of experts to contain them and develop cures to each disease before they wreak havoc within the population. 

Pandemic is a cooperative board game where players must work together using characters such as the scientist, dispatcher, and medic, to move from city to city, clearing cubes that represent each disease and collecting cards of the four corresponding colors. Collect enough cards in each color and youll be able to develop the four cures needed to win the game but beware, epidemics will pop up and diseases will outbreak and spread quickly, so time is of the essence. 

To successfully save the world and beat Pandemic will require teamwork, strategy and planning. Those who like cooperative board games with scalable difficulty should buy Pandemic and add it to their collection.

short_description:
Made by neoprene material produced and also designed anatomically. Providing local compression pad is specially designed three-point tendon silicon reduces tension. Medial or lateral is used tor epicondylitis ailments.
Indications

 The impingement syndrome of post-op
 Rotator cuff tear after repair,
 Frozen shoulder under anesthesia
after manipulation.
 Subacromial bursitis and subkorakoid.
 Used after shoulder endoprosthesis .

name: RHYTHM GRAND NOSTALGIA ENTERTAINER CLOCK 4MH838WD06
short_description: ''The Grand Nostalgia Entertainer'' Bring a touch of serenity to your home with the peaceful melodies and captivating motion of the "Grand Nostalgia Entertainer" clock.On the hour, a beautiful melody plays as the clock dial separates into three sections to reveal a rotating wheel beneath set with a star motif and five golden bells. Three multi-colored LED lights flash to the music as four Swarovski crystals sparkle on the spinning pendulum. The beautiful frame features a cherry piano finish on oak and a glass panel that will fit right in with virtually any décor. The plastic resin case houses the accurate quartz movement. Black Arabic numerals and hands indicate the time and a light sensor keeps the clock quiet when the room is dark. A volume control, on/off switch and demonstration button complete this charming clock. This is my favorite clock! It is the Rolls-Royce of the Magic Melody Motion Clock. Mike Giasi. Our cuckoo carries the traditional look and function of Black Forest style models. The Oswald is 100% made in Japan and does not use a digital cuckoo sound, but a mechanically produced sound that creates the cuckoo sound. It comes equipped with a traditional style music box that plays after the cuckoo chirps. Music Box plays Blue Danube every hour on the hour. Clock is battery quartz operated. Wooden Case Hourly Chirp Built-In Music Box Auto Night Shut-Off ON/OFF switch 1 Year Warranty 1 C Battery Included 20.7" H. x 15.4" W. 5.1 lbs. UPC # 009136422069

name: JAPANESE WALL CLOCK RHYTHM CMJ562NR06
short_description: Wall clock musical clock with a clock, in a wooden case. Metal pendulum. 16 SIP Ringtones : LISTEN 1. Fight, Westminster's melody plays every 15, 30, 45 and even hour, fight by the number of hours. 2. Melody Westminster. 3. 12 classic 4. 4 Christmas tunes. Automatic shutdown at night from 22-00 to 6-00, at 22-00 the last fight. In the mode of playing the melody in quarters (every 15 minutes), automatic switching off from 22-00 to 5-45. Adjust the volume - the sound of the melody. The watch has a quartz movement. Case: wood / brown. Demonstration mode. Batteries type C x 2 pcs. Size: 27.0 x 65.0 x 11.0cm Weight 3,4 kg.
